<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Child Care</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<%- include('header') %>
<body>
    <section class="about-container">
        <div class="about-banner">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Providing Quality Care for Your Little Ones</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-text">
                <h2>Welcome to Our Child Care Center</h2>
                <p>
                    At our child care center, we are dedicated to ensuring the well-being and happiness of every child.
                    Our team of experienced doctors and caregivers provide the best medical support, guidance, and 
                    nurturing environment for your little ones. 
                </p>
                <p>
                    Whether it's routine check-ups, expert consultations, or emergency care, we are always here 
                    to support your child's health and development.
                </p>
                <h3>Why Choose Us?</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>🏥 Expert Pediatricians and Child Specialists</li>
                    <li>🧸 Safe and Child-Friendly Environment</li>
                    <li>📞 24/7 Support for Parents</li>
                    <li>💊 Advanced Medical Care & Consultation</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="/images/Child Care Center.jpg" alt="Child Care Center">

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="founder-section">
        <h2>Meet Our Founder</h2>
        <div class="founder-info">
            <img src="/images/founder.jpeg" alt="Harsh - Founder" 
     style="border-radius: 5%;border: 5px solid rgb(110, 139 , 157); background-color: rgb(79, 115, 122);">

            <div>
                <h3>Harsh</h3>
                <p>
                    Passionate about children's health and well-being, Harsh founded this child care platform to provide
                    easy access to expert medical care and parenting guidance. With a strong vision of making health care 
                    more accessible, Harsh continues to innovate and improve services for parents and children.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mission-section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            We aim to create a world where every child receives the best health care, love, and attention they deserve.
            Our goal is to support parents in their journey of raising happy and healthy children.
        </p>
    </section>

</body>
<%- include('footer') %>
</html>
